tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_date DATE,
  interaction_notes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Emails (
  email_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  email_date DATE,
  subject VARCHAR(255),
  body TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE emails (
  email_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  email_datetime TIMESTAMP,
  email_subject VARCHAR(255),
  email_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE meetings (
  meeting_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  meeting_datetime TIMESTAMP,
  meeting_location VARCHAR(100),
  meeting_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Emails (
    email_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    email_subject VARCHAR,
    email_body TEXT,
    email_date DATE
);
